<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīmaṁnmahāmaṁḍaḷēśvara kā 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>katīyagaṇapaddēvamahārāju 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>lu pridhivi rājyaṁbu sēyucu 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṁḍaṁgānu śakhavaruśaṁbulu 
<lb n="5"/>1172 ḍagu saumyasaṁvatsara phā 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>lguṇa śu 15 gu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrītripurāṁ 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>taka dēvarapuramulōpalanu Uppu 
<lb n="8"/>veṟigi kāpulu Āṁmmi yappuḍu ve 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṭṭi suṁkamu nūvula rāmadēva vega 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ḍaku puṇyamugānu <unclear>ci</unclear>karāju li 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ccenu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
</p>

<p><hi rend="italic">Note:</hi>—The year Saumya corresponds to Ś. 1171 (expired) or Ś. 1172 (current).</p>

